{"tid":336281,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"發佈會日期確認  Nokia 8 下月 16 日登場","createTime":"2017-07-26T10:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T16:21:31.000Z","uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97ac69c8cb805fb8e7b5de0474632639a1c02b7d","tid":336281,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"發佈會將會在 8 月 16 日晚上於倫敦舉行（即香港時間 8 月 17 日 2:30am），傳聞指 Nokia 8 不但是 Nokia 重生後首部旗艦手機，亦是首部配備蔡司認證相機的 Nokia 品牌 Android 手機。Nokia 8 預計會配備 5.3 吋，解像度 2,560 x 1,440 的螢幕，搭配 Qualcomm Snapdragon 835 處理器、4GB 或 6GB RAM、64GB 儲存和雙 SIM 卡。<br />\n<br />\nHMD 將會為 Nokia 8 提供藍、銀、銅 3 色機身，前陣子有傳聞指定價會非常進取，隨時 HK$4,000 以下有交易（歐洲售價為 589 歐元，折合 HK$5,358）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4529/208615/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4529%2F208615%2F1%2F&d=wUEGWoDItWUnn4dCXV5yAP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e91a1455\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4529/208615/1/</a>"},{"pid":"93abdd3488e8c3960dee1e6bb0bc20de6783a134","tid":336281,"uid":89220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"iphone killer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb72faf104f4119fa99bd3a2785e63bdcfde988c","tid":336281,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"白牌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1068a4a94a6f43ec22c8728b8fa93840b1d9ecb2","tid":336281,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白牌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc64fbd1db9d20c766d4b3dff2